casebody.data:
STATE of Missouri, Respondent,
v.
Rebecca A. MATTHEWS, Appellant. WD 80284 Missouri Court of Appeals, Western District. ORDER FILED: JANUARY 30, 2018 Gregory L. Barnes, Jefferson City, MO, Counsel for Respondent. Marsha Irene Stiles, Springfield, MO, Counsel for Appellant. Before Division Two: Anthony Rex Gabbert, Presiding Judge, Thomas H. Newton, Judge, and Gary D. Witt, Judge

ORDER

Per Curiam:

Rebecca A. Matthews appeals from a judgment convicting her of three counts of endangering the welfare of a child in the first degree pursuant to Section 568.045, RSMo Cum. Supp. 2009. We affirm. Rule 30.25(b).
